      <nameColor>(0.65, 0.9, 0.93)</nameColor>
      <beginLetterLabel>rambunctious run</beginLetterLabel>
      <beginLetter>{0} can't sit still anymore! [PAWN_pronoun] is going to go for a run.</beginLetter>
